---

## 🎯 Insights Gained

* Weekends have higher sales compared to weekdays
* Peak order times are during afternoon and evening
* Classic category contributes the most to total sales
* Large size pizzas generate maximum revenue

---

## 📌 How to Use

1. Download the Excel file
2. Open in Microsoft Excel
3. Explore dashboard using filters and charts

---

## 💼 Use Case

This project is useful for:

* Data Analyst Portfolio
* Business Insights
* Sales Performance Analysis

